1
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:20,519
Stop right there.

2
00:01:23,919 --> 00:01:25,519
Speaking to me in that tone...

3
00:01:25,959 --> 00:01:27,040
It doesn't seem quite right.

4
00:01:27,879 --> 00:01:29,000
In order to play my part well,

5
00:01:29,879 --> 00:01:31,680
