8
00:01:38,720 --> 00:01:40,639
you really need to think hard about what to do.

9
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:43,639
Who gave you the confidence

10
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:45,800
to have such an illusion?

11
00:01:46,720 --> 00:01:48,120
This is just the beginning.

12
00:01:48,559 --> 00:01:49,639
You just have a slight...

13
00:01:49,639 --> 00:01:51,839
a tiny bit of an advantage, that's all.

14
00:01:53,839 --> 00:01:54,519
Secretary Lin,

15
00:01:56,360 --> 00:01:57,800
