20
00:02:30,160 --> 00:02:31,520
Um, let's go back to the office first.

21
00:02:41,759 --> 00:02:42,320
Come in.

22
00:02:50,160 --> 00:02:50,919
You wanted to see me?

23
00:02:51,440 --> 00:02:51,960
Well?

24
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:54,160
You talked tough before, saying

25
00:02:54,440 --> 00:02:55,639
