26
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:57,559
But aren't we meeting again now?

27
00:02:58,080 --> 00:02:59,320
Do you really have to go this far?

28
00:03:03,759 --> 00:03:05,119
If I made you feel uncomfortable,

29
00:03:05,919 --> 00:03:06,639
I apologize.

30
00:03:07,479 --> 00:03:08,559
But I really don't want to see you

31
00:03:08,559 --> 00:03:09,479
helping Gu Tiancheng anymore.

32
00:03:10,320 --> 00:03:11,039
The current situation

33
00:03:11,039 --> 00:03:12,160
is not something we can decide.

34
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:13,759
So,

35
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:15,639
