38
00:03:22,759 --> 00:03:24,479
Feimanchi should respect your authority.

39
00:03:25,919 --> 00:03:27,199
So for the upcoming work,

40
00:03:27,279 --> 00:03:27,880
I think...

41
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:29,199
Feimanchi respects your authority,

42
00:03:29,839 --> 00:03:30,800
and you should also respect

43
00:03:31,160 --> 00:03:33,000
