45
00:03:41,320 --> 00:03:42,360
This is my resignation letter.

46
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,320
I will leave tomorrow.

47
00:03:51,600 --> 00:03:52,240
Jiaqi.

48
00:03:52,919 --> 00:03:54,279
Since you don't want to see me helping Mr. Gu,

49
00:03:55,119 --> 00:03:56,279
