79
00:05:19,359 --> 00:05:20,040
Do you understand?

80
00:05:21,959 --> 00:05:22,440
Mr. Gu.

81
00:05:23,440 --> 00:05:24,559
I think in this matter,

82
00:05:24,959 --> 00:05:25,799
all the offense

83
00:05:25,799 --> 00:05:26,519
and defense

84
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,160
should be left to me.

85
00:05:28,799 --> 00:05:29,839
What gives you the right

86
00:05:29,959 --> 00:05:31,000
to fend off Feng Ziang for me?

87
00:05:32,320 --> 00:05:33,559
I'm already useless enough as it is.

88
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:34,839
Do you know that doing this

89
00:05:34,839 --> 00:05:35,959
