92
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:42,000
I saw how tired you've been lately.

93
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:44,320
And I didn't know what to do for you.

94
00:05:44,880 --> 00:05:45,440
So,

95
00:05:45,839 --> 00:05:46,559
I thought

96
00:05:46,640 --> 00:05:48,200
I should at least not be a burden to you.

97
00:05:48,880 --> 00:05:50,200
That's why I chose to handle it myself.

98
00:05:51,359 --> 00:05:52,200
Silly.

99
00:05:53,320 --> 00:05:54,279
Acting like this

100
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:56,440
