101
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:57,079
You know?

102
00:05:58,600 --> 00:06:00,000
Then why didn't you tell me?

103
00:06:00,399 --> 00:06:01,959
You looked so worried yesterday.

104
00:06:02,559 --> 00:06:03,640
It was because of Ziang, right?

105
00:06:04,440 --> 00:06:05,040
And

106
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:06,239
the investor you went to see...

107
00:06:06,519 --> 00:06:07,519
That was him too, wasn't it?

108
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:08,600
Right now,

109
00:06:08,839 --> 00:06:10,519
