110
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:11,920
Okay.

111
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:13,760
I'll compile a list for you right away.

112
00:06:24,880 --> 00:06:25,839
Jiaqi...

113
00:06:28,279 --> 00:06:30,160
How could you ever be a burden to me?

114
00:06:32,799 --> 00:06:34,679
You are a gift from heaven.

115
00:06:47,359 --> 00:06:48,679
You just said

116
00:06:49,119 --> 00:06:51,119
