117
00:06:51,559 --> 00:06:52,079
Right.

118
00:06:53,279 --> 00:06:54,600
That's the height of the bumper.

119
00:06:55,079 --> 00:06:56,480
Then why was it Du Zheng's

120
00:06:57,279 --> 00:06:58,519
knee that was shattered?

121
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:02,079
Detective Lin,

122
00:07:02,519 --> 00:07:03,480
analyze it carefully.

123
00:07:04,399 --> 00:07:05,200
If he was

124
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:07,079
hit by a vehicle with a lower bumper,

125
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:08,320
it should be

126
00:07:08,559 --> 00:07:10,000
the tibia below.

127
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:11,600
So you're saying

128
00:07:12,359 --> 00:07:13,399
it wasn't a large truck that hit him?

129
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:24,320
Gu Tiancheng.

130
00:07:27,079 --> 00:07:27,720
Detective Lin.

131
00:07:29,399 --> 00:07:30,200
What did I do?

132
00:07:31,320 --> 00:07:33,079
Do you know I've been waiting here for ages?

133
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:34,000
