135
00:07:35,279 --> 00:07:35,920
What do you want with me?

136
00:07:36,359 --> 00:07:37,480
I wanted to ask you,

137
00:07:37,880 --> 00:07:39,079
how did you know Du Zheng

138
00:07:39,440 --> 00:07:40,679
wasn't killed by a truck?

139
00:07:47,320 --> 00:07:47,959
Listen,

140
00:07:48,359 --> 00:07:49,160
Detective Lin.

141
00:07:51,959 --> 00:07:52,600
Gu Tiancheng.

142
00:07:53,320 --> 00:07:55,480
I showed the medical examiner Du Zheng's medical records.

143
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:56,559
He said

144
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:58,839
it's more likely he was hit by a car.

145
00:07:59,760 --> 00:08:00,320
You see?

146
00:08:00,640 --> 00:08:01,359
Was I right or not?

147
00:08:01,839 --> 00:08:02,839
Brilliant.

148
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:04,040
Just tell me,

149
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,519
