153
00:08:13,760 --> 00:08:14,600
Cut the crap.

154
00:08:14,799 --> 00:08:16,239
I'm being serious.

155
00:08:16,359 --> 00:08:17,440
I'm serious too.

156
00:08:17,959 --> 00:08:18,440
I...

157
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:20,480
My intuition in certain areas

158
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:21,720
is extremely accurate.

159
00:08:22,200 --> 00:08:23,959
So you should just believe what I say.

160
00:08:24,239 --> 00:08:24,880
Right, Qi Shuai?

161
00:08:25,519 --> 00:08:26,000
Right.

162
00:08:26,279 --> 00:08:26,799
Let me tell you,

163
00:08:26,799 --> 00:08:28,200
my boss's intuition is super accurate.

164
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:28,880
I can vouch for that.

165
00:08:29,359 --> 00:08:29,920
How about

166
00:08:30,239 --> 00:08:31,000
you guess for me,

167
00:08:31,519 --> 00:08:32,640
