235
00:10:26,599 --> 00:10:27,520
It seems you've done quite a bit of homework

236
00:10:28,239 --> 00:10:29,280
behind the scenes.

237
00:10:29,719 --> 00:10:31,280
But we really need to hurry.

238
00:10:31,599 --> 00:10:32,760
We must, within two days,

239
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:33,960
