240
00:10:34,760 --> 00:10:35,239
Okay.

241
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:36,840
Come home with me first,

242
00:10:37,080 --> 00:10:38,200
and then we'll go to the farm together.

243
00:10:39,799 --> 00:10:40,479
What do you mean?

244
00:10:41,119 --> 00:10:42,880
Tongzhou Factory announced they're ready to start production.

245
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:45,719
That's impossible.

246
00:10:46,400 --> 00:10:48,119
This is what my informant in the factory

247
00:10:48,119 --> 00:10:48,840
told me.

248
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:49,520
It can't be fake.

249
00:10:50,159 --> 00:10:50,840
Then tell me,

250
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:53,119
