251
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:54,640
We both overlooked one thing.

252
00:10:54,799 --> 00:10:56,320
He would go directly to the farms.

253
00:11:06,400 --> 00:11:07,320
This Gu Tiancheng

254
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,000
really has some tricks up his sleeve.

255
00:11:11,359 --> 00:11:12,320
I don't think this idea

256
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:13,479
