257
00:11:14,559 --> 00:11:15,239
We also overlooked

258
00:11:15,239 --> 00:11:16,359
a very important point.

259
00:11:16,760 --> 00:11:17,280
What?

260
00:11:18,679 --> 00:11:20,960
Nelson currently has someone by his side.

261
00:11:21,479 --> 00:11:23,039
She understands Feimanchi's operating system

262
00:11:23,039 --> 00:11:24,520
as thoroughly as you do.

263
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:26,239
And she stayed at the Tongzhou Factory

264
00:11:26,239 --> 00:11:27,559
for so many years.

265
00:11:30,039 --> 00:11:31,799
She is highly professional

266
00:11:32,119 --> 00:11:33,039
and can immediately understand

267
00:11:33,039 --> 00:11:34,520
the needs of her superiors.

268
00:11:36,239 --> 00:11:36,840
She is...

269
00:11:37,239 --> 00:11:37,799
Right.

270
00:11:38,520 --> 00:11:40,719
Gu Rongchen's secret weapon back then,

271
00:11:42,880 --> 00:11:44,559
and now Nelson's

272
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:46,400
